Application

Our High Sound Absorption Noise Reduction Polyester Fiber Foam can be used at almost any project that need acoustic treatment, such as broadcasting station, auditoriums, theaters, work spaces, air plane stations, swimming pools etc.

HuiAcoustics is a leading professional manufacturer of soundproof room divider, acoustic wall and ceiling systems in China, and has won a very high reputation within our client network after years of effort and development. We expanded our business scope of export and trade in overseas markets to strengthen our trading ability, and we have made substantial investments in human resources.

